<br>
<br>
We're actively looking for <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Monks</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Druids</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Rogues</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Bards</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Enchanters</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Requirements</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
- To be considered you must be 65 with a number of atleast 50 AA's. <br>
<br>
- You must atleast have a broadband connection.<br>
<br>
- Your character must atleast have Plane of Valor, Plane of Storm, Crypt of Decay and Bastion of Thunder flags to be considered.<br>
 <br>
- Prospects and members are expected to be active every day.<br>
<br>
- To apply, write me an email at galiaan@legacyofsteel, in which you include your current level/AA with a magelos profile. You also need to specify your computer system and connection, any additional information is accepted, especially with cross-server applicants, which should include all previous guilds.<br>
<br>
- Any questions can be directed to Galiaan, Abru or another officer if interested, leaving a post here is also accepted.<br>
<br>
<br>
These are our <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>AA requirements</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> by class:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bard</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Instrument Mastery 3, Singing Mastery 3, Epic, Combat Agility 3.<br>
Also Desired : Harmonic Attack 5, Fading Memories, Lightning Reflexes 5, Combat Stability 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Beastlord</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Spell Casting Reinforcement 3, Ambidex, Paragon, Improved Natural Durability 3.<br>
Also Desired : Beastial Frenzy 5.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Cleric</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Casting Mastery 3, Unfailing Divinity 3,  Divine Arbitration 3.<br>
Also Desired : Mass Group Buff, Radiant Cure 3, Spell Casting Reinforcement.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Druid</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Mass Group Buff, Casting Mastery 3, Radiant Cure 3.<br>
Also Desired : Innate Camo, Exodus, Spirit of the Wood 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Enchanter</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Dire Charm, Mass Group Buff, Casting Subtlety 3, Total Domintion 3.<br>
Also Desired : Casting Mastery 3, Mental Clarity 3,Gather Mana.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Magician</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Pet Discipline, Casting Mastery 3.<br>
Also Desired : Mental Clarity 3, Quick Summoning.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Monk</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Rapid Feign 3, Improved Natural Durability 3, Combat Agility 3<br>
Also Desired : Lightning Reflexes 5, Critical Mend 3, Combat Stability 3 <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Necromancer</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Lifeburn, Pet Discipline, Casting Mastery 3.<br>
Also Desired : Dire Charm.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Paladin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Improved LoH, Natural Durability 3, Combat Agility 3, Combat Stability 3, Physical Enhancement, Planar Durability 3.<br>
Also Desired : Lightning Reflexes 5, Innate Defense 5, Hand of Piety 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Ranger</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Endless Quiver, Archery Mastery 3, Combat Fury 3, Combat Agility 3, Improved Natural Durability 3.<br>
Also Desired : Fury of the ages 3, Lightning Reflexes 5, Combat Stability 3, Innate Camo.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Rogue</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Escape, Improved Natural Durability ,Chaotic Stab, Combat Agility 3, Shroud of Stealth.<br>
Also Desired: Ferocity 3, Lightning Reflexes 5.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Shadowknight</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Improved Durability 3, Soul Abrasion 3, Combat Agility 3, Combat Stability 3, Planar Durability 3, Physical Enhancement.<br>
Also Desired: Lighting reflexes 5, Innate Defense 5.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Shaman</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Cannibalization, Mass Group Buff, Casting Mastery 3, Radiant Cure 3.<br>
Also Desired : Improved Natural Durability 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Warrior</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : AE Taunt, Improved Natural Durability 3, Physical Enhancement, Combat Agility 3 Combat Stability 3,Lightning Reflexes 5, Innate Defense 5, Planar Durability 3.<br>
Also Desired: Stalwart Endurance, Tactical Mastery.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Wizard</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Most Important : Casting Mastery 3, Casting Fury Mastery 1, Casting Subtlety 3, Improved Natural Durability 3.<br>
